node.text: This morning walk in the center of Mykonos was unforgettable.You don’t have to know anyone in person. You can step in every house and feel like home. I did that and I earned more love.Amazing Myconian hospitality!

node.text:
Exercise and nutritions are like fingerprints - personalized.
My daily program starts from two room temperature glasses of still water and 4 apricots. After half an hour I drink one cappuccino and than I start my workout. After workout I eat breakfast which is 250gr steak, chickpea, lentils, beans and black rice. For lunch I’m steaming any vegetables and 250gr steak. Afternoon I have a yogurt with grapes molasses, single espresso. For dinner at 9pm I eat beetroot salad and steak. After dinner I drink only water. No more food.

node.text: Whenever you are whatever you do you can always train. No excuses 💪 Record the video of your outdoor or indoor training and send to nusret.gokce@outlook.com I will post it! Be creative! Use stone, elastic ropes, any equipment does the job ☝️important is to start your trainings! Let the oxygen flow through your veins! I will watch all of them! Let the power be with you!! 💥 you are inspiring me! Ne şartlarda olursa olsun nerede olursanız olun spora başlayın spor yapın ister spor salonunda isterseniz dışarda ister taşla ister lastikli herhangi bir ekipmanla spora başlayın ve yapmış olduğunuz sporun videolarını benimle paylaşın Ben de onları kendi Instagram hesabından paylaşmak istiyorum burdan nusret.gokce@outlook.com paylaşabilirsiniz no spor no Life #saltbae #salt #saltlife
